INSERT INTO
    ais_vessels (
    mmsi,imo_number,call_sign,name,ship_width,ship_length,ship_type,eta,draught,destination
   )
SELECT
    *
FROM
    UNNEST(
        $1::INT[],$2::INT[],$3::TEXT[],$4::TEXT[],$5::INT[],$6::INT[],$7::INT[],$8::TIMESTAMPTZ[],$9::INT[],$10::TEXT[]
    )
        ON CONFLICT (mmsi) DO UPDATE SET imo_number = COALESCE(ais_vessels.imo_number, EXCLUDED.imo_number),call_sign = COALESCE(ais_vessels.call_sign, EXCLUDED.call_sign),name = COALESCE(ais_vessels.name, EXCLUDED.name),ship_width = COALESCE(ais_vessels.ship_width, EXCLUDED.ship_width),ship_length = COALESCE(ais_vessels.ship_length, EXCLUDED.ship_length),ship_type = COALESCE(ais_vessels.ship_type, EXCLUDED.ship_type),eta = EXCLUDED.eta,draught = COALESCE(ais_vessels.draught, EXCLUDED.draught),destination = EXCLUDED.destination
